OL,3,CAt least three homes to be demolished
OL,4,Cafter 'gas explosion'
OL,6,FAt least three homes will be
OL,7,Fdemolished after a suspected gas
OL,8,Fexplosion destroyed the front of a
OL,9,Fhouse, leaving a woman seriously
OL,10,Finjured in hospital.
OL,12,FEmergency services remain on Nelson
OL,13,FStreet, in the Fishpool area of as
OL,14,Finvestigations continue into the
OL,15,Fexplosion, which happened around 11am
OL,16,Fon Wednesday 28 February.
OL,18,FA woman in her 70s was taken to
OL,19,Fhospital with serious injuries, while
OL,20,Fother residents and pupils at a nearby
OL,21,Fschool were evacuated.
