OL,6,FThe front of the house involved has
OL,7,Fbeen obliterated, with its windows
OL,8,Fblown out and most of the roof
OL,9,Fcollapsed.
OL,11,FSevere damage was caused to adjoining
OL,12,Fhomes, which are also scheduled to be
OL,13,Fdemolished.
OL,15,FIf further damage is revealed after
OL,16,Fthe demolition, a fourth house may
OL,17,Fhave to come down, another home owner
OL,18,Fhas said.
