OL,3,CAt least three homes to be demolished
OL,4,Cafter 'gas explosion'
OL,6,FMr Anwar said: "All of the house was
OL,7,Fshaking and moving up and down. We all
OL,8,Fran down towards the front door, but
OL,9,Fit had collapsed and was blocked by
OL,10,Fbricks. There was no way out.J"I
OL,11,Fthought we were going to die. We
OL,12,Fmanaged to run out of the back door.
OL,13,FAs we came out, we saw the wreckage.
OL,14,FWithin a minute, there was a huge fire
OL,15,Fcoming from next door."
OL,17,FEleven homes were evacuated on
OL,18,FWednesday, however by the evening, a
OL,19,Fnumber had been told they could return
OL,20,Fonce gas safety checks had been
OL,21,Fcarried out.
