OL,6,FLocal independent councillor Tamoor
OL,7,FTariq lives just one street over from
OL,8,Fthe destroyed house.
OL,10,FHe described the day of the blast as
OL,11,F"one of the most difficult days for my
OL,12,Flocal neighbourhood".
OL,14,FHe added: "The atmosphere's been very
OL,15,Fsomber, people have been really
OL,16,Fshocked by the events.
OL,18,F"In this close knit community, events
OL,19,Flike this are one's you hear about
OL,20,Felsewhere, not on your doorstep."
