OL,6,FA Greater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService (GMFRS) spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Firefighters have worked through the
OL,9,Fnight to damp down any remaining
OL,10,Fhotspots and ensure the safety of the
OL,11,Fsurrounding area.J"Two fire engines
OL,12,Ffrom Bolton North and Broughton fire
OL,13,Fstations are currently in attendance
OL,14,Fat the scene alongside colleagues from
OL,15,Fpartner agencies.J"We would like to
OL,16,Fthank the local community for their
OL,17,Funderstanding and support while this
OL,18,Fwork continues and investigations
OL,19,Fbegin into the cause of the
OL,20,Fexplosion."JPhil Hendrick, Head of
OL,21,FCustomer Operations (North West) at
OL,22,Fgas firm Cadent, said: "The thoughts
